Package org.hibernate.type

Interface IdentifierType<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DiscriminatorType<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BigIntegerType, BooleanType, ByteType, CharacterNCharType, CharacterType, CustomType, DateType, IntegerType, LongType, NumericBooleanType, ShortType, StringNVarcharType, StringType, TrueFalseType, UrlType, YesNoType
    public interface IdentifierType<T>
extends Type
    Additional contract for a Type may be used for a discriminator. THis contract is used to process the string representation as presented in metadata, especially in XML files.
